Skibidi Wallet Bounty
A bounty to build the first brainrot Bitcoin wallet for Gen Z and Gen Alpha

🧠 The Vibe
This is Skibidi Cash — Bitcoin meets Skibidi Toilet & TikTok Italian brainrot animals. Maximum meme, minimum friction, engineered for the TikTok-brained.

🎁 The Bounty
$6,500 USD (paid in BTC) for the best entry, judged by our legendary committee.

🚀 What To Build
Mobile-first Bitcoin wallet (Flutter or React Native)
Self-custodial, open-source (MIT license)
Use any Bitcoin SDK (LDK, BDK, Breez, Tether WDK, etc.)
Wallet must work on Bitcoin mainnet
Brutalist/meme/brainrot UX visible at EVERY step, it's never enough!
🔀 The Flow
Meme/chaotic onboarding (no email required)
Create / restore wallet
View wallet balance and recent transactions
Send Bitcoin UI
Receive Bitcoin via QR
Basic backup/restore
Can be on-chain, lightning, USDT, as long as it's non custodial!
Bonus points for weirdness, creativity, or extra features!

🫨 Join the Chaos
Have questions, want to find a partner, or just want to network and hang out? Join our Telegram group to team up, get feedback, and build in public. Introduce yourself. Everyone’s welcome.

📅 Timeline & Submission
Deadline: June 16th
Project must be open source if selected as a winner
When you're ready, submit your entry using the button below.

Submit Your Entry
All submissions must be in by June 16th. Good luck!

